modName: Clintsters Enchanting Work bench station Retexture
summary: A detailed retexture of the Enchanting work bench and station.
descriptionHtml:
Name: Clintsters Enchanting Workbench/Work Station Retexture
Version: 1.0
Category: Textures
Author: Clintster74
===============================================
Description:
A detailed retexture of the Enchanting workbench and work station.
===============================================
Installation:
Unpack the sip file to folder of your choice, copy the texture folder to your Skyrim data folder and allow for overwrite.
================================================
Uninstall:
Delete the file “enchantingworkbench01” from your Skyrim data/textures/clutter folder
================================================
Thanks to:
Bond123 for testing and input
Bethesda for the game
Nexus and of the staff for providing the best place to post and down load mods
=================================================
Tools used:
Photosopt CS5
Nifscope
================================================
Legal and licensing:
My textures are free to use in your mods without farther permission.
You may not up load my textures to other sits.
You must credit me for my work
